---
// Custom 404 page. Astro emits this as dist/404.html, which Cloudflare Pages
// serves with a real HTTP 404 status for any unmatched path — fixing the
// soft-404 (missing paths previously fell through to the homepage at 200, which
// Google/Bing flag as a soft 404 that wastes crawl budget).
//
// Deliberately STANDALONE (not the Base layout): it carries no inline <script>,
// so it needs no CSP script-src hash (scripts/check-csp-hashes.mjs only verifies
// dist/index.html, so a Base-based 404 could silently ship CSP-blocked scripts).
// Inline styles only, which the CSP allows via style-src 'unsafe-inline'.
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, viewport-fit=cover">
  <meta name="theme-color" content="#0a0a0a">
  <title>Page not found | Ophis</title>
  <meta name="description" content="The page you’re looking for doesn’t exist or has moved.">
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex, follow">
  <!-- No rel=canonical: a noindex page must not also declare itself a duplicate of
       another URL. Google ignores canonicals on 404-status responses anyway, and
       if this shell is ever served 200 by a host misconfig the lone noindex is the
       correct, non-contradictory signal. -->
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/ophis-claw-saffron.svg">
  <style>
    :root { color-scheme: dark; }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    html, body { height: 100%; margin: 0; }
    body {
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      gap: 18px; padding: 24px; text-align: center;
      background: #0a0a0a; color: #e8e8e8;
      font: 16px/1.5 system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, sans-serif;
      background-image:
        radial-gradient(420px 320px at 30% 25%, rgba(242,166,62,0.12), transparent 70%),
        radial-gradient(360px 280px at 70% 80%, rgba(140,120,255,0.10), transparent 70%);
    }
    .code { font-size: clamp(64px, 18vw, 140px); font-weight: 700; line-height: 1; letter-spacing: -0.04em; color: #f2a63e; }
    h1 { font-size: clamp(20px, 4vw, 28px); font-weight: 600; margin: 0; }
    p { margin: 0; max-width: 42ch; color: #b6b6b6; }
    .actions { display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; margin-top: 8px; }
    a.btn {
      text-decoration: none; border-radius: 10px; padding: 10px 20px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 15px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.22); color: #e8e8e8;
    }
    a.btn.primary { background: #f2a63e; border-color: #f2a63e; color: #0a0a0a; }
    a.btn:hover { border-color: #f2a63e; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="code">404</div>
  <h1>Page not found</h1>
  <p>The page you’re looking for doesn’t exist or has moved.</p>
  <div class="actions">
    <a class="btn primary" href="/">Back to home</a>
    <a class="btn" href="https://swap.ophis.fi/">Open the app</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
